Heureka has published the learning package <a href="https://www.heureka.fi/blogs/oppimateriaalit/taitava-tekoaly">Taitava tekoaly</a>. According to the page metadata and description, the material is designed as a <strong>45-90 minute</strong> teaching unit covering <strong>machine learning</strong>, <strong>AI ethics</strong>, and <strong>supercomputing</strong>.
{% endset %}
{% include "blocks/kadence/advancedheading.njk" %}

<p>Heureka describes the material as suitable for <strong>all levels of Finnish basic education</strong>. It fits well into the project's activity stream because Heureka is a consortium partner and an important public-facing environment for AI education and experimentation.</p>

